    "client_msg_id": "58f8d62e-908c-403e-80e0-82cb9413bdd6",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "So we have built something like this - basically put our platform on a mobile phone. And then made it very OS friendly (so far on iOS, and soon on Android). Which means strong integration with Siri, shortcuts, and widgets. Along with the ability to  rapidly build mini apps and share them. The platform can also respond to silent push notifications which in essence gives us server like capabilities.",
